The Streema Service may be used and accessed for lawful and non-commercial purposes only. You agree to abide by all applicable local, state, national and foreign laws, treatises and regulations, including laws governing the privacy, security and trans-border transfers of PII ((including, but not limited to, compliance with the General Data Protection (EU 2016/679) (the “
GDPR
