Streema reserves the right, in its sole discretion, at any time to modify, discontinue or terminate the Streema Service, or modify these Terms of Service without notice. If any modified terms and conditions in the revised Terms of Service are not acceptable to you, your sole remedy is to cease using the Streema Service. By continuing to access or use the Streema Service after Streema makes any such modification, you agree to be bound by the revised Terms of Service.
