Streema disclaims any and all responsibility or liability for the accuracy, content, completeness, legality, reliability, or operability or availability of information or material displayed on the Streema Service. Streema disclaims any responsibility for the deletion, failure to store, misdelivery, or untimely delivery of any information or material. Streema disclaims any responsibility for any harm resulting from downloading or accessing any information or material on the Internet through the Streema Service.
